name: PlanetKubb Scoring App

body:
### Welcome the Planet Kubb Scoring App development page.

Here will will collaborate on the latest version of the Android PlanetKubb Scoring App.  

If you would like to join the collaboration of this project, please contact me from the GitHub page.
